metadata.name: The Past Inside The Future
metadata.description: The future gleamed with a radiant promise, a utopia of technological advancement and boundless possibility. But lurking within it was the past, preserved and entombed like a time capsule from another era. Every step forward revealed another layer, another glimpse of history frozen in time, waiting to be unraveled and understood. And as the present hurtled towards that shining horizon, one couldn't help but wonder what other secrets of the past lay hidden, embedded within the fabric of the future, just waiting to be discovered.
